data.description: ENCHANTING ON ESTELLE! A delightful 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home that spans just under 1100 sq. ft. Step inside to discover a cove-style kitchen that strikes the ideal balance between style and functionality. The adjacent eat-in area is bathed in natural light, creating a bright and cheerful spot for your morning coffee or family meals. The attached 1-car garage is not merely a parking space but a versatile area equipped with a handy workbench, ready to accommodate your DIY projects or provide extra storage. Situated on a generously sized lot of .27 acres, this property offers an expansive and fully fenced back yard with a deck. This outdoor oasis provides ample space for gatherings, playtime with pets, or simply enjoying the fresh air in privacy. In addition to the inviting living spaces, this home comes with a set of newer Samsung washer and dryer. Nestled on the outskirts of town, 205 Estelle Ct provides a peaceful retreat while still being conveniently located near the heart of Hemlock. 205 Estelle Ct is not just a house; it's a canvas for your life. Whether you're envisioning cozy family moments or entertaining friends in the expansive backyard, this home is ready to accommodate your unique lifestyle. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours – contact us today for a private tour and start imagining the next chapter of your life in this captivating home.
